	Gucci Jolie    Los Angeles, Oct. 22 (PTI): Actress Angelina Jolie is in talks to take up the role of a femme fatale in a film on the Gucci fashion dynasty.  Actor Leonardo Di Caprio is being approached to play an ex-husband to Jolie rsquo;s character in the film, reports Variety magazine.  Should the deal go through, the 34-year-old actress is expected to act as Patrizia Reggiano, the former wife of Maurizio Gucci, who was sentenced to 29 years in jail for plotting Maurizio rsquo;s murder.   The film is named Gucci and will be directed by Ridley Scott. 
                                                                                                                                                                 
